<ul data-start="1676" data-end="1797">
<li data-start="1676" data-end="1731">
<p data-start="1678" data-end="1731">🔴 JavaScript errors (e.g. <code data-start="1705" data-end="1730">firebase is not defined</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1732" data-end="1759">
<p data-start="1734" data-end="1759">🟡 Warnings from Firebase</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1760" data-end="1797">
<p data-start="1762" data-end="1797">✅ Console logs like “Login clicked”</p>
</li>
</ul>
